pddl.prompt:
You are orchestrator. Integrate the following information to produce a final PDDL domain and problem targeting the FastDownwards solver:
Global goal to achieve:
{agents->orchestrator->goal}
Public environment information:
{environment->public_information}
Vowel agent contribution (their reported plan/subplan):
{plan_vowel_agent}
Consonant agent contribution (their reported plan/subplan):
{plan_consonant_agent}
Produce a PDDL domain and a PDDL problem (FastDownwards-compatible). Enclose the domain in <domain></domain> and the problem in <problem></problem>. Make explicit which actions are executable only by the vowel agent and which only by the consonant agent (for example via distinct action names or agent predicates). Model the table, block-on-block relations, and 'clear' predicate as needed. Do not assume capabilities beyond those stated by the agents and the public information.
